{"tid":791281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又嬴]壽光洪災3天 零救援如地獄 微博大量刪帖 新聞不準報","createTime":"2018-08-23T16:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T20:23:59.000Z","uid":120852,"like":153,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"74592855fe984b81d8a7bed3b2ad4db51533000c","tid":791281,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:00:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/8/23/n10660527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fgb%2F18%2F8%2F23%2Fn10660527.htm&d=RzP3LsgGeiXY4iqKetPgmv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e15f06ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/8/23/n10660527.htm</a><br />\n【大紀元2018年08月23日訊】（大紀元記者洪寧綜合報導）山東濰坊壽光因上游水庫洩洪造成河水倒灌進入市內，且淹沒了大量的蔬菜大棚、房屋，數以萬計的牲畜被淹死，至今已有3天，當地大量網民在微博上發文，氣憤地指多數是災民在自救，看不到政府救援，且媒體報導被壓制。網民在新浪微博上發布的視頻以及相關帖子被大量刪除。<br />\n<br />\n受到第18號颱風&ldquo;溫比亞&rdquo;影響，山東省出現大範圍強降雨。 20日上午，隨著上游多個水庫一起洩洪，壽光彌河河水暴漲，沿岸的村莊開始被河水倒灌，景明村、牟城村、口子村等沿岸村莊被淹，損失慘重。咆哮的洪水還吞噬了蔬菜大棚，數以萬計的牲畜被洪水沖跑，屍體已開始發臭，有村民網絡留言指，當地已經發出瘟疫預警。<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，壽光因生產蔬菜而聞名，壽光蔬菜是山東省的著名特產之一。壽光還是中共國務院命名的&ldquo;中國蔬菜之鄉&rdquo;，擁有中國最大的蔬菜生產和批發市場。<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/005PgYVfly1fujvta0eu1j30u0140n2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F005PgYVfly1fujvta0eu1j30u0140n2m.jpg&h=b4032a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/005PgYVfly1fujvtbxmxgj30u0140thl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F005PgYVfly1fujvtbxmxgj30u0140thl.jpg&h=b4520418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/005PgYVfly1fujvtfw2btj30u014010z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F005PgYVfly1fujvtfw2btj30u014010z.jpg&h=5d5d42e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/5338304733/Gw06skzfU?refer_flag=1001030103_&amp;type=comment#_rnd1535039833828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F5338304733%2FGw06skzfU%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%26type%3Dcomment%23_rnd1535039833828&d=RzP3LsgGeiXY4iqKetPgmv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fd8ec8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/5338304733/Gw06skzfU?refer_flag=1001030103_&amp;type=comment#_rnd1535039833828</a><br />\n<br />\nYY6393卿心阁  ： 网络新词语：寿光式自救 这个要是上了热榜，就有意思了！ 让全中国人看看，我们寿光，是不是被党抛弃了！ 让全中国人看看，寿光人的坚强！<br />\n回复  310<br />\n今天 14:07 来自 vivo NEX AI智慧旗舰<br />\n <br />\n人间不值得sgjh ： 他娘了个逼 政府真行 当官的真行 这个社会真行 我彻底服了这个社会的黑暗[微笑]<br />\n回复  346<br />\n今天 13:53 来自 小米Note 3 拍人更美<br />\n<br />\n官媒今天一带一路，明天雄安新区，后天又是高铁牛逼了，寿光这样了，你们媒体人有没有点人的良知呢，@央视新闻 @人民日报 @美国驻华大使馆 。#山东寿光洪灾# #寿光大雨天灾人祸#<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n热搜榜<br />\n<br />\n  国办发文规范校外培训 热<br />\n<br />\n 1.<br />\n 160万 璎珞怀孕 热<br />\n<br />\n 2.<br />\n 108万 中国队被取消成绩 热<br />\n<br />\n 3.<br />\n 88万 香蜜沉沉 男女主戏份 新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬴國萬歲"},{"pid":"fc6c3924d82dcea1faab9b0787e584f85d20d7dd","tid":791281,"uid":108467,"like":96,"dislike":11,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"如果嗰啲係人唔係豬就好了"},{"pid":"fd2a48e25c47c6bfb7afb87dd5ac7dc50c224f43","tid":791281,"uid":83582,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"CCTVB只會報外國災難"},{"pid":"3d67041242c2cc1ff72dab553c52b66512072457","tid":791281,"uid":6799,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"quote":{"pid":"fd2a48e25c47c6bfb7afb87dd5ac7dc50c224f43","tid":791281,"uid":83582,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"CCTVB只會報外國災難"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"外國冇人死都報 贏國死一萬人都唔報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0833eef325ba1756ec225b3126db0cc8b31f06","tid":791281,"uid":14423,"like":57,"dislike":15,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"見到啲豬好慘但笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c